# Sugarmagic Plan 053 — engine bundle regenerates inside the GHA
# deploy-frontend job at deploy time (it checks out the sugarmagic
# repo, runs `pnpm --filter @sugarmagic/target-web build`, then
# copies the dist here). Nothing in the game repo needs to commit
# the built bundle anymore; the top-level `dist` rule above covers
# .sugarmagic/published-web/dist/.
